<li><a href="http://thesciencenetwork.org/programs/beyond-belief-enlightenment-2-0/v-s-ramachandran" class="external text" title="http://thesciencenetwork.org/programs/beyond-belief-enlightenment-2-0/v-s-ramachandran" rel="nofollow">Ramachandran's contribution to The Science Network's Beyond Belief 2007 Lectures</a> on synaesthesia and metaphor.</li>
</ul>
